接口 MultiRandomAccessOutEdges<I extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable,E extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>

  • 类型参数:

    E - Edge value
    所有超级接口:

    HashMultimapEdges

    public interface MultiRandomAccessOutEdges<I extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable,E extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>
extends OutEdges<I,E>
    Interface for OutEdges implementations that provide efficient random access to the edges given the target vertex id. This version is for multigraphs (i.e. there can be parallel edges).
